    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i lost everything. the company is gone, the liquidators are calling every hour, and the debt is... i dont even know how to describe it. it's more than i can ever pay back. i can't go home and look my parents in the eye after all the money they helped me with. i feel like a complete ghost. there's just no way out of this shame.",
