      "content": "I am so sorry you are going through this, but please remember that your life is not defined by your debts or the company's failure. It is completely normal to feel overwhelmed and ashamed in such a situation, but you are not alone, and there are resources available to help you navigate this crisis. Consider reaching out to a financial counselor or a support group who can offer guidance and compassion during this difficult time. You deserve to be heard and supported, and there are steps you can take to move forward.",
