    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know there are resources but they dont change the reality. everything i built is dust. my family, my friends... they all saw me as this success story. now i'm just the guy who ruined everything they invested in. i feel like i'm just waiting for the world to realize i'm a fraud. it would be so much easier if i could just... stop feeling this weight. i just want the shame to go away.",
